casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Richard Carl MOENNING.
No. D-2990.
Supreme Court of the United States
June 19, 2017.
Richard Carl Moenning, of Evanston, Illinois, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
